c: 35
v: 43
t: "Tirtók kah gilteenim baaxô bagul kaxxa-mariinitaanam kee uma malah malsaanamih sabbata, uma- malah umaané le-marak-sá elle taduure mara mali. Tokkel keenik naharsi marat tekke digaalák- sá qambaalaanam maay lon? (malon) toysa Yallih madqák korsa mageytaay, Yallih madqá milagtu duddam matan"